definitions.definition: To cultivate in groves ; to grow naturally so as to form groves.
To cultivate with periodic harvesting that also serves to create order (gaps and lines of trees) to facilitate further harvesting.
To plough or gouge with lines.

main_definition: To cultivate in groves ; to grow naturally so as to form groves.
